The paper focuses on the task of identifying and labeling IP addresses in security forums, which is a problem related to cybersecurity (cs.CR). The proposed approach involves utilizing machine learning techniques for text classification and knowledge transfer across forums, which falls under the categories of information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper also deals with the problem of identifying malicious entities, which is a topic of interest in the field of security and privacy (cs.SI).
